org.dmd.dmc
Class DmcContainer

java.lang.Object
  org.dmd.dmc.DmcContainer
All Implemented Interfaces:
DmcContainerIF
Direct Known Subclasses:
DmwWrapper, DmwWrapperBase
public abstract class DmcContainer
extends java.lang.Object
implements DmcContainerIF

The DmcContainer class is a convenience base class that you can use as the default implementation of the DmcContainerIF if you wish. The intent of this strategy was to prevent lock in to a particular derivation hierarchy for those objects that wanted to use DmcObjects, but wanted to use their own base class for the wrapper. Feel free to create your own base class that implements DmcContainerIF.
